            <lg xml:id="TK87">
<l>iṉaittuṇait teṉpatoṉ ṟillai viruntiṉ</l>
<l>ṟuṇaittuṇai vēḷvip payaṉ</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>One can't say it only goes so far—whatever the measure of the guests,</l>
<l>such is the measure of the offering's reward.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
